# **INTUITION :- 
###  First of all lets see the edge cases , if egg==1 && we have to check multiple floors (f), so we need f no. of trials in worst case . As we have to take 
### maximum no of trials , so we will look into worst case . 

### if floor value i.e f==0 || f==1 then no of trials will be (0 and 1 respectively ) .

#### Now starting from lo=1 to h= f , we find mid  and if at mid it breaks 
###  calls func( mid-1 ) as it surely breaks above mid.
###  if it not breaks calls to remaining floors ( f - mid) above mid 

### Now we call both as we dont know which takes maximum no of trials 
### and then find out which is taking max trials i.e temp = 1+ max(below_mid , above_mid) 
### Makes next call such that through that it takes max no of trials

#### if(below_mid > above_mid) we will call below mid , i.e h=mid 
#### else lo = mid+1

